	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You shape the image of a small scene, bringing to life what appears in your mind as you stretch a small piece of fleece slightly in your hand, the illusion stretching and taking form over the area you choose.</em></p><p dir=\"auto\" id=\"viewer-nmest4883\"><strong>Illusory Image</strong></p><p>Roll an &amp;Reference[illusoryimages]{illusion check} for this spell.</p><ul><li aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"auto\"><p id=\"viewer-1nbdk4884\">You create an illusion of an object, a creature, or some other visible phenomenon that is no larger than a 15-foot cube. The image is purely visual; it isn't accompanied by sound, smell, or other sensory effects.</p></li><li aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"auto\"><p><strong>Concentration:</strong> While within 120 ft. of the image, once on each of your turns, you can cause the image to move up to 30 ft. The image shifts dynamically, and appears to be moving in a manner of your choosing (such as a person walking).</p></li></ul>",
